# eca_search
- 例: 入力1234567890の場合
```
rest: 661905584 = 1234567890 - 572662306
rest: 89243278 = 661905584 - 572662306
rest: 112958 = 89243278 - 89130320
rest: 31038 = 112958 - 81920
rest: 9193 = 31038 - 21845
rest: 455 = 9193 - 8738
rest: 135 = 455 - 320
rest: 7 = 135 - 128
rest: 2 = 7 - 5
rest: 0 = 2 - 2
```
